     and human-readable definitions.

   - New SNANA user Emille Ishida found many format bugs 
     using compiler at IPMU (and snana v9_02).
     Make minor fixes in
        snana.car  snlc_fit.car  sntools.c  sntools.h 
        snlc_sim.c  kcor.c  
