  v9_35 [April 11, 2011]

       !!! switch from F77 to gfortran !!!

   - combine_fitres.c :
     replace large arrays XVAR8 and XNTVAR with pointers
     and dynamically alloate in function fitres_malloc().
     Program size is now 130 MB, x10 smaller than before.

