      See INPUTS.IPAR_SIMSED_SHAPE, INPUTS.IPAR_SIMSED_COLOR
      SIMSED_PARAM key is equivalent to 
        SIMSED_SHAPEPAR
        SIMSED_COLORPAR
        SIMSED_COLORLAW
      so that sntools_grid know which SIMSED params are what.

