        SNDATA.XTINC_MILKYWAY[ifilt_obs]
        GENLC.XTINC_MILKYWAY[ifilt_obs]
     since MWgaldust returns an array of extinctions only
     for SDSS ugriz. Noticed by Kyle & Ravi.

