      for &SNLCINP SNFIELD_LIST, allow the following
      to all work the same way,
         SNFIELD_LIST = 'E1', 'E2', 'S1', 'S2'
         SNFIELD_LIST = 'E1 E2 S1 S2'
         SNFIELD_LIST = 'E1 E2', 'S1 S2'
      This allows using the command-line override to specify
      multiple fields.

