         v10_42d (Jan 19 2016) 

         ***** IMPORTANT(v10_42d) ***** 

         ***** USEFUL(v10_42d) ***** 

         ***** MISCELLANEOUS(v10_42d) ***** 

   snlc_sim.c, sntools_fitsio.c : write SIM_REDSHIFT_HOST to data files
 
