       although parabolic (approx) errors look OK:
         NDATA~1000, NBIASCOR~3E6, redchi2_tol=.001
       MINOS errors empirically fixed by
          - reducing NBIASCOR to 1E6, or
          - increasing redchi2_tol=0.002 (1 less fit iteration)


