         v10_50 (Jun 19, 2017) 

         ***** IMPORTANT(v10_50) ***** 
 
   + Fixed synthetic SPECTROGRAPH fluxes with SNR_ZPOLY option.
   + New lensing section in manual, Sec 4.14.2

